00:31:48,916 --> 00:31:53,067
You know, just recently we've had these Israeli attacks on

258
00:31:53,048 --> 00:31:56,152
on Palestine and on the West Bank, you see.

259
00:31:56,413 --> 00:31:57,634
So there were people there.

260
00:31:57,934 --> 00:31:59,297
I mean, they're in dangerous positions.

261
00:31:59,317 --> 00:32:04,825
They know they're dangerous, but some innocent people, you see, their lives have just been blown out.

262
00:32:04,884 --> 00:32:05,244
That's it.

